  <brief_title>Ambu AuraGain Laryngeal Mask Airway and I-gel in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Comparison of Ambu AuraGain (Original Name of Product) Laryngeal Mask Airway and I-gel in Children</official_title>
  <sponsors>
