  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Children aged below 7 years are randomly assigned to AuraGain Group or I-gel group. After
      anesthetic induction, AuraGain or I-gel is inserted and mechanical ventilation is started.
      Oropharyngeal leak pressure, peak inspiratory pressure, success rate for insertion, ease for
      insertion, ease for gastric tube insertion and fiberoptic bronchoscopic views will be
      compared between two groups.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
